name: Guide
description:
Among my friends there are extraordinary people ... These are the people of the Giants, the Heroes of our time.

One of these Giants is Ilya Shi, a guide to the quantum world of ideas and spirits, a yogi, a collector of bright people.

Today I made a sculpture from the new series "Neo Heroes", which I dedicate to him.
Shine brighter and brighter Friend!


"Guide" from the Neo Heroes series
